snippet.title: BANDITS PreAlpha 1/4 - Natalia
snippet.description:
https://benerot.com/bandits.html
TanKrovia is a tank brawl battle arena for 2-4 players locally on pc.
The current version has 4 different tanks to choose from. of 8 that we prototyped with.
The game will be open developed closely with whoever wanna be part of our community.
